---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="How It Works | CookTwo" description="From download to dinner in 5 steps. See the real user flow of CookTwo, the collaborative adaptive nutrition app for couples.">

  <section class="section-padding bg-cream">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <span class="badge-signature mb-6 inline-block">How It Works</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6">From download to dinner<br class="hidden md:block" /> in 5 steps</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">The real flow of CookTwo. Set up once, cook every day. Here's exactly what happens when you and your partner start using the app.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="space-y-24 md:space-y-32">

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-sage flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">1</div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">Create Your Kitchen</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mb-4">Set up your personal profile in about 2 minutes. This is what makes CookTwo work for <em>you</em> specifically.</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 space-y-3">
              <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">What you enter:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Name</strong> — so your partner sees you, not "User A"</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Dietary preferences</strong> — Vegetarian, Vegan, Keto, Paleo, Gluten-free</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Allergies</strong> — peanuts, shellfish, dairy, etc.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Body goals</strong> — Lose weight, Maintain, Build muscle, Just eat well</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Body metrics</strong> — weight, height, age, gender, activity level</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sage font-medium mt-4 text-sm">Takes about 2 minutes. This feeds the AI that calculates your personalized portions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <img src="/images/steps/step-1-invite.webp" alt="Step 1 - Create your kitchen profile" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <img src="/images/steps/step-2-goals.webp" alt="Step 2 - Link with your partner" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-sage flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">2</div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">Link With Your Partner</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mb-4">One person gets a 6-digit invite code. The other enters it. That's it — you're connected to the same household.</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 space-y-3">
              <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">What happens:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Share a <strong class="text-text-primary">6-digit invite code</strong> with your partner</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Partner enters the code in their app</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Both profiles linked to <strong class="text-text-primary">same household</strong></span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Real-time sync</strong> starts immediately</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sage font-medium mt-4 text-sm">No accounts to merge. No friction. One code, one kitchen.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-sage flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">3</div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">Stock Your Pantry</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mb-4">Tell CookTwo what you already have. Type naturally — the AI understands you.</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 space-y-3">
              <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">How it works:</p>
              <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-border font-mono text-text-secondary text-sm">
                <span class="text-sage">You type:</span> "chicken, 2 cups rice, spinach, half an onion"
              </div>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mt-2">The AI parses your input, categorizes each item (Proteins, Grains, Vegetables, etc.), estimates quantities, and adds everything to your shared pantry.</p>
              <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm mt-2">Or skip this step entirely and add items later directly from your shopping list.</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sage font-medium mt-4 text-sm">Natural language input. No dropdowns, no forms. Just type what you have.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <img src="/images/steps/step-3-pantry.webp" alt="Step 3 - Stock your pantry" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <img src="/images/steps/step-4-generate.webp" alt="Step 4 - Shop together" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-sage flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">4</div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">Shop Together</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mb-4">One shared grocery list with real-time sync. Both partners see changes instantly.</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 space-y-3">
              <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">What you get:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>One <strong class="text-text-primary">shared grocery list</strong> with real-time sync</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>AI auto-categorizes into <strong class="text-text-primary">7 categories</strong> (Produce, Dairy, Proteins, Grains, Condiments, Frozen, Other)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Quick-add chips</strong> for items you buy regularly</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">"Done Shopping"</strong> moves everything to your pantry automatically</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sage font-medium mt-4 text-sm">Add milk at home. Partner sees it at the store. Under 100ms sync.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-sage flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">5</div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary">Cook Together</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mb-4">Generate a meal via AI chat. Get personalized plating per partner. Same recipe, different portions, different macros.</p>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-xl p-6 space-y-3">
              <p class="font-semibold text-text-primary">The magic moment:</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Chat with AI: <strong class="text-text-primary">"What can we make with chicken and rice?"</strong></span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>AI generates a recipe using <strong class="text-text-primary">your pantry items</strong></span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span>Each partner gets <strong class="text-text-primary">personalized portions</strong> based on their goals</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5 text-sage flex-shrink-0" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                  <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Same recipe, different macros</strong> — cook once, eat together</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sage font-medium mt-4 text-sm">Cook one meal. Plate it two ways. Everyone hits their goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <img src="/images/steps/step-5-cook.webp" alt="Step 5 - Cook together" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-border" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-cream-dark">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="badge-live mb-6 inline-block">The Daily Loop</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-4">Set up once. Cook every day.</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary max-w-2xl mx-auto">CookTwo gets smarter the more you use it. Here's the self-reinforcing cycle that runs in your kitchen.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 items-center">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"/><path d="M3.27 6.96 12 12.01l8.73-5.05"/><path d="M12 22.08V12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Your Pantry</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">What you have right now</p>
          </div>

          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sage" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </div>

          <div class="md:hidden flex justify-center py-2">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sage rotate-90" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-terracotta/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" x2="12" y1="19" y2="22"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">AI Suggests Meals</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Based on what's in stock</p>
          </div>

          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sage" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </div>

          <div class="md:hidden flex justify-center py-2">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sage rotate-90" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 items-center mt-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-sage" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="8" cy="21" r="1"/><circle cx="19" cy="21" r="1"/><path d="M2.05 2.05h2l2.66 12.42a2 2 0 0 0 2 1.58h9.78a2 2 0 0 0 1.95-1.57l1.65-7.43H5.12"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Missing Items → Shopping List</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">Auto-added when meal is generated</p>
          </div>

          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sage" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </div>

          <div class="md:hidden flex justify-center py-2">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sage rotate-90" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" x2="19" y1="12" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-terracotta/10 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-terracotta" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 2 3 6v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h14a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V6l-3-4Z"/><path d="M3 6h18"/><path d="M16 10a4 4 0 0 1-8 0"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-text-primary mb-1">Shop Together</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">"Done Shopping" moves to pantry</p>
          </div>

          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sage" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8"/><path d="M21 3v5h-5"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16"/><path d="M8 16H3v5"/></svg>
          </div>

          <div class="md:hidden flex justify-center py-2">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-sage rotate-90" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8"/><path d="M21 3v5h-5"/><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16"/><path d="M8 16H3v5"/></svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg">The cycle repeats. <strong class="text-text-primary">Your pantry gets smarter. Meals get better. Zero waste.</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-sage">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to cook together?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">Set up your shared kitchen in under 5 minutes. Start with the free tier — no credit card needed.</p>
      <a href="/#get-early-access" class="inline-block bg-white text-sage px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-lg font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-cream shadow-lg">Get Started Free</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
